title: SVN bindings for Perl?
comment: <p>Maybe using the Perl bindings would grant the same degree of interoperability that Subversion itself has?  (Might even be microscopically more efficient -- just think of the extra fork() you'd save ;)</p><p>I've been thinking of using the Ruby-Svn bindings for the same reason, though it would obviously be nice to avoid the extra dependancy and just use what's already provided by the platform.</p>
