title: Re: SVN bindings for Perl?
comment: <p>David,</p><p>Yes, switching to the SVN bindings is on my list—or at least optionally doing it when they're available. But they are so poorly documented and I've had so few tuits that it hasn't been worth it, yet.</p><p>In the meantime, there must be some simple way to do this in Windows. I need to find the win32-porters list and ask there, I guess.</p><p>—Theory</p><p>PS: CVSspam rocks!</p>
